    "name": "Ease Single Inn",
    "detail": "1. A very clean hostel. There is women's' only wing, and guys' only wings. The kitchen is very neat and tidy. Have 24H coffees, teas, juices, bicuits. I am impressed by the toilet. The way they hang the toothpaste is so creative. But some people might not have deep sleep, as there is a night club at the 12th floor. (the hostel is located at the 10th floor) 2. Staffs are very friendly. Before check in at 3pm and after check out at 11am (my friend and I came back later to pick our luggage after 8pm), they allow you to store your luggage at the receptionist counter. Th e hostel has a cute white pet dog. 3. Very convenient to tour around Taichung city The hostel is 5 mins walk from Taichung Railway Station/ Taichung Bus Terminal. Right at the entrance of this hostel is the bus stop 'First Square' 第一廣場. This is the bus stop after the Taichung Railway Station bus stop. 4. Many shops nearby, also immigrant shops especially Vietnamese and Indonesian shops.",
